|- type_params_opt typeconstr_name = constr_decl1 | ... | constr_decln and </typedefi//i/> gives E, (typeconstr_name : kind) and E' and E''@EB1,...,EBn

{{ com
A variant type definition yields two sorts of bindings: one for the type
